Uses of Package
jmarkov.solvers

  • Packages that use jmarkov.solvers 
    Package Description
    jmarkov
    Provides the basic elements to model continuous time Markov chains (CTMC).
    jmarkov.solvers
    Provides classes for customizing a solver used by JMarkov to solve transient and steady state probabilities in different models.
  • Classes in jmarkov.solvers used by jmarkov 
    Class and Description
    GeometricSolver
    Abstract class that defines a Geometric solver for QBD processes
    SteadyStateSolver
    An abstract class for steady state solver.
    TransientSolver
    An abstract class for Transient solvers.
